{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC08_HAR_630.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1f,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hello, Marietta. I had a question for you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, about that story... I've heard it so many times, I know more than I want to."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, I knew it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Actually, there's more to that story.<CR>I don't really care for it,<CR>but...wanna hear it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "There might be something related to the snack, so please tell me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Then, I'll just brieeefly go over it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Young Harry received all that love from his mother, gained knowledge and experience, and inherited the business."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Young Harry showed a rare talent for business, and became the wealthiest man in town."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "He fell in love with a beautiful lady, and everything seemed to be going well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "It's like a fairytale..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x161,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "But, that didn't continue for long."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x38,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Wow, I'm starting to get nervous!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "A few years later, they had their last and biggest crop failure, and the town was in deep trouble."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "It was like 20 years ago, so I was too young to really remember..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "But my mom seemed to be going through a tough time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x161,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Now, Young Harry, who had received all that love from his mother, didn't hesitate to open up his safe."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "He sacrificed his entire savings to gather enough food to share with the people who were starving..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "And thanks to him, this town was able to survive the crisis."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "But he paid a big price for that,<CR>and Harry's Trading House was on<CR>the verge of going out of business."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "But with all of Young Harry's strenuous efforts, it was somehow able recover."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "And that led to what you see today."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "So something like that happened...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I guess. I think it's a good story,<CR>but seeing Mr. Owner now, it sounds<CR>kinda fake."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "If that story is true, then he's my personal savior, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I guess that story didn't really<CR>help at all... Anyway, about the<CR>snack Mr. Owner's mother made..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I heard it was made from grounded up beans. It was a really simple baked good."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "I guess it was popular among the mothers back then to make it for their children."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "But, I'm sure they made it with whatever ingredients they had, so I'm sure it'll be hard to recreate."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "But just knowing what kind of snack it was is very helpful. Thank you so much!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "(Okay, I should go back to Mr. Fred's one more time!)"
        }
    ]
}